              <div id="workiz" class="mb-10 border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-white">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl">1. Workiz</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Best for Replacing ST's Call Tracking</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="score-badge high">57</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                  If the main ServiceTitan feature you actually use is call tracking and lead attribution, Workiz is the closest replacement. It has a built-in VoIP phone system that tracks calls, records them, and automatically creates leads from missed calls.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                  <strong>Switching from ServiceTitan:</strong> The phone number porting process takes 1-2 weeks. Workiz can import your customer data via CSV. The dispatch board is comparable to ServiceTitan's, though the reporting is less deep.
                </p>
                <div class="cta-box">
  <h3>Try Workiz Free</h3>
  <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-foreground)]/70 mb-4">Built-in call tracking replaces one of ServiceTitan's best features.</p>
  <a href="#" class="cta-button" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank">Learn More →</a>
</div>
              </div>

              <div id="jobber" class="mb-10 border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-white">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl">2. Jobber</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Easiest and Most Affordable Alternative</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="score-badge high">56</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                  Jobber is the simplest and most affordable option. It does not try to replace everything ServiceTitan does — instead, it focuses on doing the basics exceptionally well. If you are switching because ServiceTitan is too complex and too expensive, Jobber is the cleanest break.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                  <strong>Switching from ServiceTitan:</strong> The easiest migration of any alternative. CSV import, clean interface, minimal training needed. Most teams are operational in 1-3 days. The trade-off is losing dispatch board depth and call tracking.
                </p>
                <div class="cta-box">
  <h3>Try Jobber Free</h3>
  <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-foreground)]/70 mb-4">The simplest path away from ServiceTitan. Operational in a day.</p>
  <a href="https://go.getjobber.com/bo42cjptz4m2" class="cta-button" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank">Learn More →</a>
</div>
              </div>

              <div id="fieldedge" class="mb-10 border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-white">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl">3. FieldEdge</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Best for QuickBooks Desktop Users</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="score-badge mid">53</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                  FieldEdge is the strongest alternative for HVAC companies that rely on QuickBooks Desktop (not Online). Its two-way sync with QB Desktop is the best in the industry. However, customer service has received mixed reviews recently.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                  <strong>Switching from ServiceTitan:</strong> FieldEdge's feature set is comparable to ServiceTitan's for core operations. The main advantage is the QB Desktop integration. The main risk is customer support quality — verify current support response times before committing.
                </p>
                <div class="verdict-strip">
                  <p class="text-sm"><strong>Non-affiliate link:</strong> <a href="https://fieldedge.com/pricing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary underline">See FieldEdge pricing</a></p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div id="service-fusion" class="mb-10 border border-border rounded-lg p-6 bg-white">
