                  Service Fusion's unlimited-user pricing model is the opposite of ServiceTitan's per-technician model. If per-user fees are the main reason you are leaving ServiceTitan, Service Fusion eliminates that problem entirely.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-foreground/80 mb-4">
                  <strong>Switching from ServiceTitan:</strong> The feature set covers core operations but lacks call tracking and marketing attribution. The interface is less modern. The value proposition is purely financial — predictable pricing with no per-user surprises.
