</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div id="faq">
              
            </div>

            <div id="verdict" class="mt-10">
              <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mb-4">Verdict</h2>
              <div class="prose">
                <p>
                  <strong>Workiz</strong> is the best overall ServiceTitan alternative if call tracking is your must-have — it replaces one of ServiceTitan's strongest features natively. <strong>Jobber</strong> is the easiest and most affordable path if you want simplicity and fast setup. <strong>Service Fusion</strong> is the pick if per-user fees are your biggest pain point.
